event_name: DJs Enda and Lionel at Rhythm City Strut
location: Rhythm City Strut, 2474 Prince Edward St, Vancouver, BC, Canada, British Columbia V5T 1W8
description: This is a 3-hour social dance event featuring DJ Enda The Night (Enda Tan) followed by DJ Lionel (Lionel Ackiana) at Rhythm City Strut. Event hosted by Rhythm City Productions. Dancer Spotlight: Ruth 'Sugar' Sullivan.
